<p>Peter Momtchiloff, who retired from his long-held position as philosophy editor at <a href="https://global.oup.com/academic/category/arts-and-humanities/philosophy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Oxford University Press</a> at the end of 2023, has been brought on by <a href="https://www.lexacademic.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Lex Academic</a>, a firm that helps its clients with various aspects of academic publishing.<span id="more-54026"></span></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class=" wp-image-54027 aligncenter" src="https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/momtchiloff-peter-photo.png" alt="" width="339" height="375" srcset="https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/momtchiloff-peter-photo.png 800w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/momtchiloff-peter-photo-271x300.png 271w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/momtchiloff-peter-photo-768x849.png 768w, https://dailynous.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/momtchiloff-peter-photo-400x442.png 400w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 339px) 100vw, 339px" /></p>
<p>Momtchiloff will be associate publication consultant at Lex Academic, according to an <a href="https://www.lexacademic.com/blog/peter-momtchiloff/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">announcement</a> from the firm.</p>
<p>You can listen to a podcast episode produced by the Aristotelian Society in which Momtchiloff discusses his thirty years at OUP <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/jm/podcast/peter-momtchiloff-on-thirty-years-at-oup/id504195948?i=1000683293034" target="_blank" rel="noopener">here</a>.</p><p>The post <a href="https://dailynous.com/2025/06/02/momtchiloff-consulting-for-lex-academic/">Momtchiloff Consulting for Lex Academic</a> first appeared on <a href="https://dailynous.com">Daily Nous</a>.</p>